HEADWORD: Trisection
<hw>Tri*sec"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>trisection</ets>.]</ety> <def>The division of a thing into three
parts, Specifically: <fld>(Geom.)</fld> the division of an angle into
three equal parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Triseralous</ent>⟦br⟧
